3c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHovering over an element reveals a purple box around its boundaries. Clicking your cursor and dragging over elements shows a translucent purple box indicating the selected elements, while individual elements retain a purple boundary. This helps you visualize which elements are selected or not.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eYou don’t have to drag over the entire area of each element you wish to select, just so long as any part of each element falls within your dragged boundary, it will appear within your selected area.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"click-and-shift-to-select\"\u003e\n            Click and Shift to Select\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf the elements you wish to select and group have other elements in their way—for example, you want to select all background elements but no text elements—you cannot simply drag your cursor, or you’ll select the unwanted elements.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Select Elements in Canva\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/select-elements-in-canva.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInstead, click your cursor on the first element you want to select, then press and hold the \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e key while continuing to click on other elements. Holding down \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e while clicking adds multiple elements to your selection group. Once you’ve selected them all, let go of \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo deselect individual elements, simply click the element from the group while still holding \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e. You can mix and match both methods of selection to add or remove elements to your selected group. Although all these features are found in Canva’s free version, you might want to \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/canva-free-vs-canva-pro/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econsider upgrading to Canva Pro\u003c/a\u003e for more features.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eOnce you know how to select your elements, it’s time to group them together. There’s more than one way to group elements using the browser version of Canva.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"use-the-group-and-ungroup-buttons\"\u003e\n            Use the Group and Ungroup Buttons\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Canva Click and Drag to Group\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-group.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are many \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/hidden-canva-features/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehidden features in Canva\u003c/a\u003e, but grouping is not one of them; the Group button is easily visible.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWith two or more objects selected, the floating toolbar appears by your selection. This toolbar features the Group button alongside \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/top-canva-ai-tools/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003erelevant Canva AI tools\u003c/a\u003e, Duplicate, Lock, Delete, and More. Selecting \u003cstrong\u003eGroup\u003c/strong\u003e will set your selected elements into a group together.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Canva Click and Drag to Ungroup\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-click-and-drag-to-ungroup.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eUngrouping is just as easy. Select any element from the group and select Ungroup. Ungrouping your Canva group will return each element to an individually movable and independent element.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"right-click-to-group-and-ungroup\"\u003e\n            Right-Click to Group and Ungroup\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSelect the elements you wish to group, then right-click and choose \u003cstrong\u003eGroup\u003c/strong\u003e from the menu.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Canva Browser showing the Right-Click menu and Group highlighted\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-group.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe reverse works for ungrouping your objects: \u003cstrong\u003eright-click\u003c/strong\u003e your group and choose \u003cstrong\u003eUngroup\u003c/strong\u003e from the options. This, again, returns your previously grouped elements to independent elements once more.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                \n                                    \n                                                \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1680\" height=\"840\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Canva Browser Right-Click Ungroup\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/canva-browser-right-click-ungroup.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"group-and-ungroup-with-the-keyboard-shortcut\"\u003e\n            Group and Ungroup With the Keyboard Shortcut\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe final way to group elements in Canva’s browser version is probably the most intuitive for designers—we sure love our keyboard shortcuts. First, select multiple objects, then hit \u003cstrong\u003eCmd\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eG\u003c/strong\u003e (Mac) or \u003cstrong\u003eCtrl\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eG\u003c/strong\u003e (Windows) to group your elements in the blink of an eye.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo ungroup with the keyboard shortcut, there’s just one extra key: Shift. Select your group and hit \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eCmd\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eG\u003c/strong\u003e (Mac) or \u003cstrong\u003eShift\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eCtrl\u003c/strong\u003e + \u003cstrong\u003eG\u003c/strong\u003e (Windows) to return your elements to their independence.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eEven grouped elements can still be individually edited by double-clicking the specific element. For example, if you have a textbox within your group, double-click on the text box to edit the text. The same goes for \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/canva-change-color-of-image-graphics-text/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eimage elements you wish to further edit\u003c/a\u003e or even move; just double-click the individual element to make it editable, but it remains part of the group once done.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_30\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eIf you’re \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/canva-how-to-use-layers/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eusing layers in Canva\u003c/a\u003e, remember that grouping elements on different layers will group the layers together. For example, if you need your layers in a specific order, grouping elements from the top and bottom, but not the middle, of the layers will re-order your layers once grouped. It’s something to keep in mind.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-group-and-ungroup-elements-in-the-canva-app\"\u003e\n                        How to Group and Ungroup Elements in the Canva App\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Canva app is a great option for designing on the go, but it does work differently than Canva’s web version. Let’s see how you can select, group, and ungroup elements on the Canva app for mobile or tablet.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"selecting-elements-in-the-canva-app\"\u003e\n            Selecting Elements in the Canva App\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSince the Canva app uses touch technology, selecting elements is a little different from being able to use the cursor or Shift key on the browser version.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo select one individual element on the Canva app, tap the element once until a purple box surrounds it.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eAfter selecting the first element, the floating toolbar should appear. Tap “\u003cstrong\u003e…\u003c/strong\u003e” which opens the \u003cstrong\u003eMore\u003c/strong\u003e menu \u0026gt; choose \u003cstrong\u003eSelect Multiple\u003c/strong\u003e. Then tap on any other elements you wish to select; each element will have a purple box, and the group of selected elements will be bound in a white-dotted box. The Select Multiple menu action also denotes how many elements are selected in red, so you can keep track.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_38\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eTo deselect, simply tap anywhere else on your Canva artboard.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"how-to-group-elements-in-the-canva-app\"\u003e\n            How to Group Elements in the Canva App\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen multiple elements are selected, you’ll already be in the \u003cstrong\u003eMore\u003c/strong\u003e menu, which is where you’ll find the Group tool.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eTap \u003cstrong\u003eGroup\u003c/strong\u003e, and the white-dotted boundary line with however-many-selected-elements-in-purple-boxes turns into one large purple box denoting the grouped element created. This is denoted again by the number on \u003cstrong\u003eSelect Multiple\u003c/strong\u003e, which now reads as \u003cstrong\u003e1\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eTo ungroup elements in the Canva app, select the group, and the floating toolbar now offers the option to \u003cstrong\u003eUngroup\u003c/strong\u003e. If it doesn’t appear, select the \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003e...\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34; in the floating toolbar and choose \u003cstrong\u003eUngroup\u003c/strong\u003e from there instead.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
